s for steam tracing solutions control and monitoring systems for electric tracing of pipes tanks hoppers and instrument sampling systems turnkey solutions that provide solutions for heat tracing including design optimization installation and ongoing maintenance products and services such as heating sensing monitoring controlling and calibration tools and temporary electric power distribution and lighting products receive news  ratings via email  enter your email address below to receive a concise daily summary of the latest news and analysts ratings with marketbeatcoms free daily email newsletter leave a reply cancel reply your email address will not be published required fields are marked comment name  email  website more news jefferies upgraded mccormick nysemkc from hold to buy in a report released today just yesterday mccormick nysemkc traded  shore capital reiterated tate lyle plc lontate to hold in a report released today shore capital has reiterated tate lyle spirit airlines nasdaqsave has been upgraded from neutral to buy in a statement by citigroup earlier today boasting a price of  spirit fevertree drinks plc lonfevr has been retained to hold in a statement by shore capital earlier today having a price of gbx fevertree keybanc upgraded logmein nasdaqlogm from sector weight to overweight in a report released today only yesterday logmein nasdaqlogm traded  shore capital reiterated st jamess place plc lonstj to buy in a report released today yesterday st jamess place plc lonstj citigroup upgraded seaworld entertainment nyseseas from sell to neutral in a report released today citigroup has upgraded seaworld entertainment nyseseas gigamon nysegimo price target increased to  issued a research note today by da davidson in a report issued  da jefferies upgraded jm smucker nysesjm from hold to buy in a report released today just yesterday jm smucker nysesjm traded xl group plc usxl has been upgraded from neutral to overweight in a statement by jpmorgan earlier today jpmorgan has upgraded xl group plc about breaking finance news contributors contact privacy policy copyright   breaking finance news thermon group holdings inc thrn company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile thermon group holdings inc thrn related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialselectrical components  equipment overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse thrn on new york stock exchange usd pm edt change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description thermon group holdings inc incorporated on march   is a provider of engineered thermal solutions for process industries the company offers a range of products such as heating cables tubing bundles and control systems and services such as design optimization engineering and installation and maintenance services the company operates through four segments based on four geographic countries or regions united states canada europe and asia the companys thermal solutions also referred to as heat tracing provide an external heat source to pipes vessels and instruments for the purposes of freeze protection temperature and flow maintenance environmental monitoring and surface snow and ice meltingthe company offers a range of electric heat tracing cables steam tracing components tubing bundles and instrument and control products as well as various complementary product lines the companys product portfolio includes selfregulating and power limiting heating cables which automatically change heat output as pipe temperature changes as well as constant wattage heating cables mineral insulated mi cable skin effect trace heater heat traced tube bundles for environmental gas sampling systems heat transfer compounds and steam tracers for steam tracing solutions control and monitoring systems for electric tracing of pipes tanks hoppers and instrument sampling systems turnkey solutions that provide customers with solutions for heat tracing including design optimization installation and ongoing maintenance products and services such as heating sensing monitoring controlling and calibration tools and temporary electric power distribution and lighting products used in energy infrastructure construction projects and maintenance and turnaround projectselectric heat tracing applicationsthe company manufactures components of an electric heat tracing system including heating cables control and monitoring systems and heating systems for tanks and hoppers the company also offers various electric heating cables including conductive polymer selfregulating heating cables and power limiting cables the companys htsx selfregulating heating cable is suitable for heat tracing applications involving crude oil and various chemicals the tek and htek series resistance constant watt heating cables are used where circuit lengths exceed the limitations of parallel resistance heating cables miq mineral insulated heating cables are used for high temperature maintenance high temperature exposure and high watt density applications miq cables are composed of a high nickel or chromium alloy sheath the companys thermtrac system is designed to heat a pipeline of approximately  miles long from a single power pointsteam heat tracingthe company offers range of heat transfer compounds as well as steam tracers and tubing bundles that provide its customers with steam tracing solutions the companys heat transfer compounds create a thermal connection between the heat tracing system and the process equipmenttemperature controls and monitoringthe company supplies a range of control and monitoring products from mechanical thermostats to microprocessorbased systems that control and monitor the status of electric heat tracing systems the company provides individual units for projects as well as multipoint controllers that can be integrated into and communicate with a plants central data management and control system the company offers a range of temperature control monitoring systems as part of its tracenet family of controllers tracenet controllers allow the operator to assess operating control parameters and operating conditions throughout the heat tracing system network utilizing its tracenet control solutions the companys controllers can communicate with approximately  controllers over  channels allowing approximately  heat trace circuits to be monitored within the same networkinstrumentationthe company is engaged in providing preinsulated and heattraced tubing bundles with accessories the companys range of products includes both electric and steamheated bundles containing various types of tubing such as copper stainless steel and polymerhopper heatingthe companys product ht hopper heating module is a selfcontained heater designed for operation on surfaces prone to vibration the ht hopper heating module has various flow paths for electrical currentturnkey servicesthe company provides customers with various solutions for their heat tracing needs its services include project planning product supply engineering services system integration installation commissioning and maintenancedesign and engineering servicesthe company offers heat tracing design and engineering services during every stage of a project the company provides design and engineering services to its customers through its staff of engineers and technicianssumac temporary power productsthe company through sumac fabrication company limited sumac offers power distribution panels master or slave subpanels power cords and lighting fixtures sumacs line of products and solutions are designed to provide a means of supplying temporary electrical power distribution and lighting at energy infrastructure facilities for construction and during maintenance and turnaround projects at operating facilities sumacs products are sold to end users operating in various markets including heavy industrial settings oil and gas refining and upgrading power generation plants petrochemical production facilities and mining operationsthe company competes with pentair plc » full overview of thrn company address thermon group holdings inc  thermon drsan marcos   tx    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation charles sorrentino  bruce thames  jay peterson  eric reitler  james pribble  » more officers  directors thermon group holdings inc news briefthermon group files for mixed shelf of up to  mln jun   briefthermon reports q adjusted earnings per share  may   briefthermon group says unit to start production in greater moscow region in  feb   briefthermon reports q adjusted earnings shr feb   » more thrn news related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialselectrical components  equipment thermon group holdings inc thr company profile  reuterscom x edition united states africa américa latina عربي argentina brasil canada  deutschland españa france india italia  méxico россия united kingdom united states profile thermon group holdings inc thr related topics stocksstock screenerindustrialselectrical components  equipment overview news key developments people charts financials analysts research pulse thr on new york consolidated usd  jul  change  chg   prev close  open  days high  days low  volume  avg vol  wk high  wk low  full description thermon group holdings inc incorporated on march   is a provider of engineered thermal solutions for process industries the company offers a range of products such as heating cables tubing bundles and control systems and services such as design optimization engineering and installation and maintenance services the company operates through four segments based on four geographic countries or regions united states canada europe and asia the companys thermal solutions also referred to as heat tracing provide an external heat source to pipes v