for any solar related application solar thermal power solar thermal power concentrates heat from the sun the concentrated solar power heats oil which is used to produce steam oil is heated to °c °f in the piping before being heated by the gathered solar energy to produce steam recommended heat trace system thermon miq mineral insulated heating cable molten salt needs to be maintained at °c °f to keep it from solidifying recommended heat trace system thermon miq mineral insulated heating cable freeze protection is required on all steam and cooling water piping recommended heat trace system thermon bsx selfregulating heating cable for the cooling water and thermon miq for the steam and condensate lines photovoltaic photovoltaic cells directly convert sunlight into electricity electrons in the cells become excited when they are struck by sunlight generating dc power which is converted into ac power for distribution photovoltaic cells are produced from raw material called polysilicon polysilicon production plants use water for cooling along with other chemicals to control by products recommended heat trace system thermon bsx selfregulating heating cable for freeze protection of the water piping and htsx for process temperature maintenance about thermon news wikis sitemap international sites terms of use copyright disclaimer privacy statement iso  thermon products reps only investor relations  languages home products applications design  support faq contact us about us products overview corporate brochure industrial electric heat tracing steam heat tracing instrument tubing bundles cems  analyzer umbilicals commercial electric heat tracing controls and monitoring selfregulating cables complex piping design guide powerlimiting cables parallel constant watt cables series constant watt cables mineral insulated heating cables skin effect systems tank insulation tank and hopper heating controls and monitoring systems accessories design  support more product information bsx™ r